xxl.core.collections.queues
Interface LIFOQueue<E>

Type Parameters:
E - the type of the elements of this queue.
All Superinterfaces:
Queue<E>
All Known Implementing Classes:
FileStackQueue, StackQueue
public interface LIFOQueue<E>
extends Queue<E>

The interface LIFO queue represents a LIFO (last in, first out) iteration over a collection of elements (also known as a sequence) with a peek method. This interface predefines a LIFO strategy for addition and removal of elements.

See Also:
Queue
